List example with short description and example code. Specify if it's HTML, CSS, or JavaScript for clarification.

Ex #1: Conditional Logic (Hide/Show image example) - Code starts with a hidden image and shows/hides when a button is clicked.

HTML Context:
<button id="toggleImageBtn">Show Image</button>

<img id="myImage" src="https://via.placeholder.com/200" 
     alt="Example Image" style="display: none; margin-top: 10px;">

<script src="script.js"></script>

JS Code:
const btn = document.getElementById('toggleImageBtn');
const img = document.getElementById('myImage');

btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
  if (img.style.display === 'none') {
    img.style.display = 'block';
    btn.textContent = 'Hide Image';
  } else {
    img.style.display = 'none';
    btn.textContent = 'Show Image';
  }
});
